<TEXT>
   MCorp has agreed to sell its majority-owned MTech
computer services unit to Electronic Data Systems Corp. for $281
million in cash and securities.
   The pact signed Monday supersedes a $234 million tentative
agreement reached last month with an investment group headed by
Robert M. Bass of Fort Worth.
